From Karen Black Subject Re Happy Easter Ranck writes Nick Pettefar wrote English cars Rover Reliant Morgan Bristol Rolls Royce Talk about Harleys using old technology these Morgan people really like to use old I think their suspension design hasn't changed since they went from wheels to back in the ' And it's not like they had reached the pinnacle of good design at that point Well if you want to pick on Morgan why not attack its ash wood frame or its hand bent metal skin just try and get a replacement I thought the kingpost suspension was one of the Mog's better Karen Black